            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#JP">
                <p>Purchase of the doctor Phelik (Felix), for one holoktinos (solidus), with Petros, Markiasnos and Methios witnessing.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>For the cost of purchase, cf.  IG14.142 (<ref target="https://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000959">ISic000959</ref>)</p>
